# ── Glean .gitignore ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Principle: the repo is PUBLIC by default. Anything that must never be
# published is excluded here, so exclusion is enforced by the repo, not
# by remembering. See docs/DATA_HANDLING.md.

# ── Never publish: private planning + third-party copyrighted material ──
# planning docs, research PDFs, anything not for the world
_private/

# ── Never publish: real reconnaissance data ──
# Raw tool output and scan results about real infrastructure are sensitive
# even for domains you own. Commit only sanitised fixtures, deliberately.
raw/
scans/
*.scan.json
targets.txt
targets.md
**/live-*.json

# ── Secrets / config ──
.env
*.key
config/*.local.*
**/secrets.*

# ── Python (for when development starts) ──
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.venv/
venv/
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.pytest_cache/

# ── OS / editor noise ──
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
